text: The Chinese Taipei women's national handball team is the national team of Chinese Taipei. It is governed by the Chinese Taipei Handball Association and takes part in international handball competitions. ==Asian Championship record== * 1987 – 5th * 1989 – 4th * 1991 – 5th * 1993 – 6th * 1995 – 4th * 1997 – 5th * 1999 – 5th * 2000 – 7th * 2002 – 5th * 2004 – 4th * 2012 – 7th ==External links== * *IHF profile Category:Women's national handball teams Handball National team
title: Chinese Taipei women's national handball team
